---
import Button from "./Button.astro";
---

<section id="contact" class="py-20 relative overflow-hidden" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0170B9 0%, #6366F1 50%, #8B5CF6 100%);">
  <!-- Decorative circles -->
  <div class="absolute -top-20 -left-20 w-80 h-80 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 w-96 h-96 bg-white/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center reveal relative z-10">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
      清掃業務のDXを、今日から始めませんか？
    </h2>
    <p class="text-blue-100 text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      無料トライアルで、CleanAIの便利さをぜひ体験してください。導入のご相談もお気軽にどうぞ。
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-8">
      <Button
        href="#"
        variant="primary"
        class="bg-white! from-white! to-white! text-primary! hover:bg-gray-100! shadow-[0_0_30px_rgba(255,255,255,0.3)] text-lg px-8 py-4"
      >
        無料で資料をダウンロード
      </Button>
      <Button
        href="#"
        variant="outline"
        class="border-white! text-white! hover:bg-white/10! hover:text-white! text-lg px-8 py-4"
      >
        お問い合わせ
      </Button>
    </div>

    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-blue-100">
      <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
          stroke-width="2"
          d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"
        ></path>
      </svg>
      <span class="font-medium">お電話でのお問い合わせ:</span>
      <span class="font-bold text-white">03-1234-5678</span>
      <span class="text-sm">(平日 9:00〜18:00)</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
